    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001299_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right">Pearl,
<lb/>near <placeName>Sierra Leone </placeName>
<lb/><date when="1858-03-25"><hi rend="sup underline">25</hi> March
<lb/>1858</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Robert,</salute></opener>
<lb/><p>We have been going
<lb/>at the rate of 200 miles a day
<lb/>ever since we left <placeName>Liverpool</placeName>
<lb/>and have been much favoured
<lb/>by a kind provdidence in
<lb/>the weather poor <persName>Oswell</persName> was
<lb/>sorely sick while rolling
<lb/>through the <placeName>Bay of Biscay</placeName>
<lb/>and eat nothing for about
<lb/>three days but we soon

	<pb facs="liv_001299_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>got away from the ice &amp;
<lb/>snow to beautiful summer
<lb/>weather, and we are getting
<lb/><unclear cert="medium">nearly</unclear> thawed. We sleep
<lb/>with all our portholes open
<lb/>and are glad of the morning
<lb/>by day - At night we see
<lb/>the Southern <unclear cert="medium">cross</unclear> and the <!--Are these geographic tags?-->
<lb/>pole star which stands
<lb/>so high over you is here
<lb/>so low we cannot see
<lb/>it for the haze - We shall
<lb/>not see it again but
<lb/>the same Almighty gracious
<lb/><del type="strikethrough">f</del>Father is over all and
<lb/>is near to all who love him

	<pb facs="liv_001299_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>you are now alone in the
<lb/>world and must seek his
<lb/>friendship and guidance
<lb/>for if yo do not lean
<lb/>on him you will go
<lb/>astray and find that the
<lb/>way of <unclear cert="medium">trangsgression</unclear> is
<lb/>hard. The Lord be
<lb/>gracious to you and
<lb/>accept you though un -
<lb/>worthy of his favour</p>
<lb/><p>you must write 
<lb/>to me for if you do not
<lb/><!-- faded --> continue to write

	<pb facs="liv_001299_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>to you <persName>Oswell</persName> says he will
<lb/>gather some shells for you
<lb/>we land today but it is
<lb/>only to <app><rdg cert="medium">cool</rdg><rdg>coal</rdg></app> and then we
<lb/>go to the cape - we <!--place?-->
<lb/>shall be there before
<lb/><persName>Uncle John Moffat</persName>
<lb/>Mama &amp; <!-- group of people? -->Oswell's love
<lb/>to you - My kind regards
<lb/>to your master &amp; Mistress
<lb/>if <term type="nationality">French</term> is not too
<lb/>much for you it might
<lb/>be added to <term type="nationality">Latin</term> &amp; <term type="nationality">Greek</term>
<lb/>but your master will
<lb/><w><gap extent="2" unit="chars"/><supplied cert="high">kn</supplied>ow</w> best
</p>

            </div>
